THERE IS no doubt that King Monada's song Malwedhe has taken Mzansi by storm. Just like an infectious disease, Malwedhe #IdibalaChallenge is even spreading to overseas countries such as China. Back home, the #IdibalaChallenge has infected almost everyone - from motorists, school children, paramedics, nurses and it is now a wedding step. The challenge has inspired a dance like never before in Mzansi. And the good thing about the #IdibalaChallenge, is that one does not have to be a good dancer to take part in it.   